algonquin.cst2335.finalproject_fall23.SongViewModel
public class SongViewModel extends androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
ViewModel for managing and storing song data throughout the lifecycle of the application. This ViewModel holds a list of songs and the currently selected song. * @author Lei Luo * @version 1.1
